    "path": "src/agent/task",
    "name": "task",
    "purpose": "Owns agent task runtime state. Task keeps public construction, preview, worker routing, and direct session_tx event sending in task.rs via send_status_event and in task_step.rs via send_step_event, imports Step from the top-level step module, tracks inserted steps with TaskState::step_count, stores parsed Plan records with their StepSignature list in TaskState::plan_list, keeps private step behavior in task_step.rs, and keeps execution routing in task_execution.rs. route_step_event parses Plan output with Plan::parse, runs ready steps, and records (plan, signatures); run_step rejects unit Intent steps before insertion, enforces the ten-step limit, and assigns authoritative step numbers.",
